PN,39401
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773399918
OL,3,C'Penny-pinching' budget cuts by NHS
OL,4,Care destabilising services, BMA
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FDoctors in Cheshire and Merseyside are
OL,8,Fwarning that "penny-pinching" budget
OL,9,Fcuts by NHS England are putting
OL,10,Fpatient lives at risk and
OL,11,Fdestabilising services.
OL,13,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,14,Fsays financial restrictions imposed on
OL,15,FIntegrated Care Boards (ICB) have led
OL,16,Fto recruitment freezes, staffing
OL,17,Freductions, limits/bans on agency
OL,18,Fworkers and cuts to overtime pay
OL,19,Facross the region.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773399918
OL,3,C'Penny-pinching' budget cuts by NHS
OL,4,Care destabilising services, BMA
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FA survey by BMA found 88% of doctors
OL,8,Fbelieve the cuts are harming patient
OL,9,Fcare, with many saying they are
OL,10,Foverwhelmed and uncovering an unsafe
OL,11,Fnumber of patients.
OL,13,FIf the matter is not resolved, 92% of
OL,14,Fdoctors support formally entering a
OL,15,Ftrade dispute, while 80% of doctors
OL,16,Fsupport taking industrial action if it
OL,17,Fis understood to be necessary.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773399918
OL,3,C'Penny-pinching' budget cuts by NHS
OL,4,Care destabilising services, BMA
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FDoctors are saying they are
OL,8,F"overwhelmed" and that morale amongst
OL,9,Fstaff is at an all-time low, with many
OL,10,Fleft to cover unmanageable patient
OL,11,Fnumbers with staffing cover that does
OL,12,Fnot meet required safe levels.
OL,14,FA doctor working in the Cheshire and
OL,15,FMerseyside region who qualified two
OL,16,Fyears ago, said: "Currently staffing
OL,17,Flevels feel really unsafe.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@MO]xD@ROU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773399918
OL,3,C'Penny-pinching' budget cuts by NHS
OL,4,Care destabilising services, BMA
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,F"As a second year doctor, I have had
OL,8,Fshifts where I have been responsible
OL,9,Ffor 30 very poorly patients on my own,
OL,10,Fall while being pulled in every
OL,11,Fdirection to different departments.
OL,13,F"It takes so long to get through them
OL,14,Fall that it's leaving patients with
OL,15,Fpotentially life-threatening
OL,16,Fconditions waiting to be seen for up
OL,17,Fto 8 hours.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773399918
OL,3,C'Penny-pinching' budget cuts by NHS
OL,4,Care destabilising services, BMA
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,F"It's such an overwhelming situation
OL,8,Fto be in and you know that you aren't
OL,9,Fgiving patients the best care, but
OL,10,Fit's out of your hands. What we need
OL,11,Fis more doctors on shift, but these
OL,12,Fcuts to pay mean these shifts just
OL,13,Faren't being filled."
OL,15,FAccording to the BMA, there has been a
OL,16,F27% reduction in pay for routine and
OL,17,Fessential extra work undertaken by
OL,18,Fdoctors, which they say has caused
OL,19,Fless people opting to pick up those
OL,20,Fextra shifts, unsafe staffing levels,
OL,21,Fputting patient safety at risk.
OL,26,@uD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773399918
OL,3,C'Penny-pinching' budget cuts by NHS
OL,4,Care destabilising services, BMA
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FDue to low staffing levels,
OL,8,Fconsultants are warning that they are
OL,9,Fbeing stretched to cover the shifts of
OL,10,Fmore junior doctors. This is causing
OL,11,Froutine surgery and treatment to be
OL,12,Fcancelled to enable consultants to
OL,13,Frest.
OL,15,FOf the resident and SAS doctors who
OL,16,Fresponded to the survey, 84% said
OL,17,Ftheir health, wellbeing and working
OL,18,Fconditions had worsened because of the
OL,19,FICB and NHS England's approach.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773399918
OL,3,C'Penny-pinching' budget cuts by NHS
OL,4,Care destabilising services, BMA
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FA specialty registrar working in the
OL,8,FCheshire and Merseyside region said:
OL,9,F"Morale is at an all-time low. By the
OL,10,Fend of my shifts, I am so exhausted
OL,11,Fthat I am struggling to make the life-
OL,12,For-death decisions expected of me, but
OL,13,Fwhen I get home, I can't sleep because
OL,14,FI am so worried about it all playing
OL,15,Fout again on my next shift.
OL,17,F"I have had several shifts when I was
OL,18,Fthe only registrar, when we are meant
OL,19,Fto have at least two to meet safe
OL,20,Fstaffing standards.
OL,26,@qD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773399918
OL,3,C'Penny-pinching' budget cuts by NHS
OL,4,Care destabilising services, BMA
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,F"The pressures and responsibilities
OL,8,Fthat fall on my shoulders are simply
OL,9,Ftoo demanding to cope without support.
OL,10,FThe problem won't be solved when
OL,11,Fdoctors are expected to take a pay cut
OL,12,Fto deal with these demands."
OL,26,@tD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773399918
OL,3,C'Penny-pinching' budget cuts by NHS
OL,4,Care destabilising services, BMA
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FWarning about impact on consultants
OL,8,Fand the destabilisation of patient
OL,9,Fcare, Dr Den Langhor, BMA Mersey
OL,10,Fregional consultants committee chair
OL,11,Fand a consultant working in
OL,12,FMerseyside, said: "We have taken this
OL,13,Fstand to protect not only staff across
OL,14,FCheshire and Merseyside, but to keep
OL,15,Fpatients safe, so they can get the
OL,16,Fquality of care they deserve. Make no
OL,17,Fmistake that the ICB's drive to save
OL,18,Fmoney comes with the very real cost of
OL,19,Fpatient safety.
OL,26,@tD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773399918
OL,3,C'Penny-pinching' budget cuts by NHS
OL,4,Care destabilising services, BMA
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,F"Consultants in the Cheshire and
OL,8,FMersey region are being forced to plug
OL,9,Frota gaps, overseeing busy wards with
OL,10,Fnot enough staff.
OL,12,F"This is having a catastrophic impact
OL,13,Fon hospital capacity, destabilising
OL,14,Fservices and seriously compromising
OL,15,Fpatient care.
OL,17,F"The ICB must reverse these hugely
OL,18,Fdamaging funding cuts that hit staff
OL,19,Fand patients' staff most of all."
OL,26,@oD@AOU{D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773399918
OL,3,C'Penny-pinching' budget cuts by NHS
OL,4,Care destabilising services, BMA
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,FCalling on the ICB to reserve cuts to
OL,8,Fpay and ensure safe staffing levels
OL,9,Ffor doctors, Dr Kartik Goyal, co-chair
OL,10,Fof the BMA's Mersey regional resident
OL,11,Fdoctors committee, said: "Resident
OL,12,Fdoctors are working themselves to the
OL,13,Fbone, going above and beyond their
OL,14,Fnormal hours in impossible
OL,15,Fcircumstances trying to keep patients
OL,16,Fsafe.
OL,18,F"The demands are putting them at risk
OL,19,Fof burnout, but their hard work and
OL,20,Fdedication have been rewarded with
OL,21,Flots of trusts cutting overtime rates.
OL,26,@sD@ZOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1773399918
OL,3,C'Penny-pinching' budget cuts by NHS
OL,4,Care destabilising services, BMA
OL,5,Cdoctors say
OL,7,F"Inevitably, this means a
OL,8,Fsignificantly lower uptake in extra
OL,9,Fshifts and leaving unsafe rota gaps.
OL,10,FThese cuts must be reversed so we can
OL,11,Fhave safe staffing levels and doctors
OL,12,Fcan provide the quality of care that
OL,13,Fpatients in Cheshire and Mersey
OL,14,Frightly expect."
OL,16,FNHS Cheshire and Merseyside's
OL,17,FIntegrated Care Board has been
OL,18,Fapproached for comment.
OL,26,@vD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
